<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Little2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Little,</orth> adv. not much, in a small degree: <cit><quote>our own doth l. advantage,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.1.34" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 1, 34</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>has done l. better,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.197.34" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 197</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I love him so l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.4.206" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. II, 4, 206</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>recking as l. what betideth him,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.3.40" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 40</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mm 4.3.166" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 3, 166</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 2.1.318" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 1, 318</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 1.2.23" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 2, 23</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 2.142.23" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 142</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.1.147" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 1, 147</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 1.2.95" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. I, 2, 95</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 1.5.190" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 5, 190</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 1.1.17" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 1, 17</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 3.1.17" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 17</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 3.1.116" default="NO" valid="yes">John III, 1, 116</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 5.1.64" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 1, 64</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.1.36" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 1, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.349" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 349</bibl> etc.
